BioGen Business Website

A simple responsive business website inspired by a real-world healthcare company website.
This project was built using HTML and CSS as a frontend practice project to improve my web development and UI design skills.

Features
Responsive business-style layout
Navigation bar with company details
Hero banner section
About, Vision, and Mission sections
Product showcase images
Contact call-to-action section
Clean and structured UI design
Technologies Used
HTML5
CSS3
Purpose of the Project

This project is completely hardcoded and was created for learning and practice purposes.
The main goal was to improve my understanding of:

Page structuring using HTML
Styling and layouts using CSS
Flexbox positioning
Business website design patterns
Building real-world frontend interfaces
Learning Outcome

By building this project, I gained hands-on experience in creating professional-looking business websites and improving frontend development fundamentals.

